<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20150228215354/http://www.zeit.de/wissen/geschichte/2015-02/index?base_date=2015-02">Februar</a> | <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20150228215354/http://www.zeit.de/wissen/geschichte/2015-01/index?base_date=2015-01">Januar</a> | <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20150228215354/http://www.zeit.de/wissen/geschichte/2014-12/index?base_date=2014-12">Dezember</a> | <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20150228215354/http://www.zeit.de/wissen/geschichte/2014-11/index?base_date=2014-11">November</a> | <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20150228215354/http://www.zeit.de/wissen/geschichte/2014-10/index?base_date=2014-10">Oktober</a>
