<li class="last"><h3><a title="Datenspionage - Die Kabel-Krake, die alles weiß" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20150228215354/http://www.zeit.de/wissen/2013-06/seekabel-glasfaser-spionage" id="hp.centerpage.teaser.mosaik.1.4.4./2013/15/hitler-tagebuecher/seite-6"><strong>Datenspionage </strong><span class="shorttitle">Die Kabel-Krake, die alles weiß</span></a></h3></li>
